# Add to Leaderstat

## Description

Adds a value to a player's leaderstat.

#### Available to

* [x] Scripts
* [ ] LocalScripts
* [ ] Yields

## Inputs

#### Player (Object)

Player that you want to get the leaderstat from.

* [x] Can use Variable

```
game.Players.Roblox
```

#### StatName (String)

Name of the stat you want to get from the leaderstat.

* [x] Can use Variable

```
Cash
```

## Outputs

#### Value (Number)

Returns the current leaderstats value of the given player.

```
PlayerCash
```
